---
import SiteLayout from "../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";

const jsonLd = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Organization",
  name: "PoE2 Hub",
  url: "https://poe2hub.net",
};
---
<SiteLayout
  title="About PoE2 Hub"
  description="PoE2 Hub is a community guide site for Path of Exile 2, covering build guides, boss fight breakdowns, league mechanics, and free tools like the Build Planner and Chromatic Orb Calculator."
>
  <h1>About PoE2 Hub</h1>

  <h2>What is PoE2 Hub</h2>
  <p>
    PoE2 Hub is a community guide platform for Path of Exile 2. We put together build guides,
    boss fight breakdowns, league mechanic explainers, and practical tools, cross-checked
    against official sources and established community guides rather than assembled from
    guesswork. The goal is straightforward: give players a direct answer without wading through
    ten tabs of forum threads to get there.
  </p>

  <h2>Our Tools</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong><a href="/build-planner/">Build Planner</a></strong> — pick your class and Ascendancy, get an instant gear, gem, and passive tree recommendation.</li>
    <li><strong><a href="/chromatic-calculator/">Chromatic Orb Calculator</a></strong> — exact probability and expected orb cost for any socket color combination.</li>
    <li><strong><a href="/loot-filter-generator/">Loot Filter Generator</a></strong> — answer a few questions, get a working .filter file, no syntax knowledge required.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Content Coverage</h2>
  <p>
    As of the current patch, PoE2 Hub covers 13 boss fight guides, 22 build guides across every
    live Ascendancy, and 10 in-depth league mechanic breakdowns, alongside a class guide, trade
    guide, unique item reference, and skill gem reference. Content is updated to track current
    patches, each page carries a version note showing what it was last checked against.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions, corrections, or feedback: <a href="mailto:contact@poe2hub.net">contact@poe2hub.net</a>
  </p>

  <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
  <p>
    PoE2 Hub is an independent fan-run site and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Grinding
    Gear Games. Path of Exile 2 is a registered trademark of Grinding Gear Games. All game
    content, item names, and artwork referenced on this site remain the property of their
    respective owners.
  </p>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(jsonLd)} />
</SiteLayout>

<style>
  h2 { margin-top: var(--space-3); }
  ul { color: var(--text-dim); padding-left: 1.2em; }
  li { margin-bottom: 0.5em; }
  p { color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.75; }
</style>
